title: American Horror Stories: Ryan Murphy Writes for Cody Fern and Dylan McDermott
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I hope they do AHS stories: Salem about the witches origins and the original supreme! ❤️
I just want to see the Countess say to Michael “you have a jaw line for days” if they revisited him going to the Cortez in Apocalypse but for AHStories🥰😂🤞🏻🤞🏻

I would like a Madison episode where we see her trying to escape hell. I would love if she figures out to escape on her own.

Speaking of Madison I am rewatching coven and when Madison and Zoe bring back Kyle.  Madison says Azazel, we submit to you body and soul, we offer you our obedience and everlasting devotion until death sanctifies this unholy Union. Then Zoe says did we just marry the devil?    Do you think this is why Madison got sent to hell? It sounds like she made a deal with the devil.
Cody Fern and Dylan McDermott would make some pretty hot vampires.
I am WAY too excited for this show ! every week will be like a different season !
